reviewText: Buy the award winning movie "Cromwell" with Charles Gray. It is only $10. The movie is great. This particular Phoenix Group dvd is, "i kid you not," 30 minutes of the exact 1971 movie, "Cromwell," for 5 times the price. Phoenix group plays 30 minutes of the movie for you and adds in about 3 or 4 extra voice-over comments. The end. Not worth a fifth of what i paid.
